{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of alert"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSAlert","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"AlertComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of borders ("},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProviders","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and sizes (from "},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllAlertComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent05AlertB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B33ThemeAlertComponentTokensProviderC","symbolKind":"class","title":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Class"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for alert component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomAlertComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the alert component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeIcon: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._100 }","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.outOfSystem75 }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomAlertComponentTokensProvider: AlertComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(alert: CustomAlertComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(alert: CustomAlertComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let alertComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own semantic tokens providers","    let alertComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider(","                    sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokens